16
00:02:25,420 --> 00:02:29,590
♪I run towards you♪

17
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:31,950
♪In the dark valley♪

18
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:33,910
♪You will catch my heart♪

19
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:37,270
=The On1y One=

20
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:40,270
