00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,290
Grab your chopsticks and dig in.

567
00:37:18,660 --> 00:37:20,160
- Yummy.
- Really?

568
00:37:20,160 --> 00:37:22,500
Mmm, tasty.

569
00:37:27,410 --> 00:37:29,370
Tian, is it tasty?

570
00:37:29,910 --> 00:37:30,750
Mmm.

571
00:37:33,080 --> 00:37:34,040
Look at you.

572
00:37:34,040 --> 00:37:36,620
I thought I might have
poisoned the food.

573
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:39,290
Why the long face?

574
00:37:42,660 --> 00:37:44,250
If I smiled while eating,

575
00:37:44,250 --> 00:37:45,540
you'd think it was weird, right?

576
00:37:49,250 --> 00:37:50,660
Yeah, yeah. Alright.

577
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:53,370
You totally set me up for that.

578
00:37:58,250 --> 00:37:59,370
Oh, right.

579
00:37:59,370 --> 00:38:00,910
Mute, come and give me a hand.

580
00:38:01,950 --> 00:38:03,620
The shrimp's defrosted.

581
00:38:03,620 --> 00:38:05,200
Let's peel them. Hurry up.

582
00:38:05,200 --> 00:38:07,790
Come on, stop eating.

583
00:38:44,290 --> 00:38:45,250
Do you have a stomachache?

584
00:38:51,120 --> 00:38:53,660
No, I just ate too much.

585
00:39:10,290 --> 00:39:11,450
Where's your bracelet?

586
00:39:16,410 --> 00:39:17,250
It broke.

587
00:39:22,330 --> 00:39:23,540
Does that bother you?

588
00:39:24,950 --> 00:39:26,450
If so,

589
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:28,330
then tell me,

590
00:39:31,200 --> 00:39:33,830
did you lie to Old He and Yang Jing
like this in the office?

591
00:39:44,370 --> 00:39:45,210
(Yes,)

592
00:39:46,410 --> 00:39:47,370
(that's it.)

593
00:39:48,250 --> 00:39:49,580
(It's like my pseudomyopia.)

594
00:39:50,040 --> 00:39:51,500
(I just need to correct it.)

595
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:05,700
I said,

596
00:40:06,870 --> 00:40:09,370
did you lie to them like this
in the office?

597
00:40:10,620 --> 00:40:12,290
About what?

598
00:40:16,200 --> 00:40:17,580
About screwing up your exam.

599
00:40:25,080 --> 00:40:26,370
That was an important exam.

600
00:40:27,290 --> 00:40:29,540
Why would I mess it up on purpose?

601
00:40:29,950 --> 00:40:31,410
It wouldn't have done me any good.

602
00:40:45,910 --> 00:40:47,040
Where are you going?

603
00:41:16,700 --> 00:41:17,660
When are you moving?

604
00:41:22,290 --> 00:41:24,120
When are you going to Class B?

605
00:41:29,250 --> 00:41:30,090
At noon.

606
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:34,620
I'll go before the lunch break ends.

607
00:41:35,830 --> 00:41:38,120
I'll go back later.

608
00:41:47,290 --> 00:41:48,910
I really messed up.

609
00:41:50,450 --> 00:41:52,200
I made mistakes in every subject.

610
00:41:54,330 --> 00:41:55,170
Seriously.

611
00:42:02,780 --> 00:42:06,600
♪Cold clouds wake up
the scorching thunderstorm♪

612
00:42:08,410 --> 00:42:13,160
♪Little by little, I float into droplets♪

613
00:42:16,660 --> 00:42:20,660
♪I watch a movie alone, and walk back
with no one to share my umbrella♪

614
00:42:22,270 --> 00:42:27,150
♪Bitterness turns sighs into night♪

615
00:42:42,720 --> 00:42:45,910
♪Far away♪

616
00:43:01,700 --> 00:43:02,540
Here.

617
00:43:07,870 --> 00:43:09,540
It's already too crooked.

618
00:43:11,700 --> 00:43:14,580
You've got to snap off the bent part.

619
00:43:14,580 --> 00:43:16,580
Only then can new buds sprout

620
00:43:17,200 --> 00:43:18,870
and fresh, beautiful leaves grow back.

621
00:43:37,540 --> 00:43:39,750
They'll go another class later.

622
00:43:39,750 --> 00:43:42,330
Yeah, the school's being
really strict this time.

623
00:43:42,330 --> 00:43:44,080
Can't we ask the teacher to reconsider?

624
00:43:44,620 --> 00:43:45,660
It's okay.

625
00:43:45,660 --> 00:43:47,250
It's only a few weeks until finals.

626
00:43:47,250 --> 00:43:48,540
They'll fight their way back.

627
00:43:48,540 --> 00:43:50,620
Not sure if they can make it.

628
00:43:50,620 --> 00:43:51,910
They will.

629
00:43:51,910 --> 00:43:53,540
They definitely will!

630
00:43:54,160 --> 00:43:56,250
But isn't this what we always say

631
00:43:56,250 --> 00:43:58,200
when someone leaves?

632
00:43:58,200 --> 00:43:59,700
But how many actually

633
00:43:59,700 --> 00:44:00,540
come back?

634
00:44:00,540 --> 00:44:02,410
Little Mouth Xu, get it together!

635
00:44:02,620 --> 00:44:03,540
Sheng.

636
00:44:05,950 --> 00:44:07,830
Class, get back to your self-study.

637
00:44:07,830 --> 00:44:08,950
Let's go back to our seats.

638
00:44:09,540 --> 00:44:10,540
Keep it down.

639
00:44:10,540 --> 00:44:12,910
- I'm just being honest.
- Sheng, you too,

640
00:44:12,910 --> 00:44:13,830
