641
00:44:14,330 --> 00:44:16,500
Oh, but don't push too hard,

642
00:44:16,500 --> 00:44:18,370
or next time, you'll be the one
comforting me.

643
00:44:21,620 --> 00:44:27,920
♪I want to tell you,
it's more than just loneliness♪

644
00:44:28,500 --> 00:44:34,800
♪At least let an affectionate soul
solve this puzzle♪

645
00:44:34,900 --> 00:44:38,260
♪That encounter finally
turned into an ending♪

646
00:44:38,270 --> 00:44:41,740
♪Reason lost to a few so-called whys♪

647
00:44:41,740 --> 00:44:47,520
♪A tear silently rolls down my palm♪

648
00:44:47,660 --> 00:44:53,560
♪Pain is a question from happiness♪

649
00:44:56,680 --> 00:44:59,060
(Class 2B)

650
00:45:07,330 --> 00:45:08,170
Tian!

651
00:45:08,660 --> 00:45:09,620
It's Tian.

652
00:45:09,790 --> 00:45:11,120
How could he come to Class B?

653
00:45:11,580 --> 00:45:13,250
Tian's just helping someone else.

654
00:45:13,540 --> 00:45:14,790
He's really got some pull.

655
00:45:15,370 --> 00:45:16,330
Which seat?

656
00:45:16,580 --> 00:45:17,620
Hey, sit here.

657
00:45:18,080 --> 00:45:19,160
I've got it ready for you.

658
00:45:27,550 --> 00:45:28,490
He's so handsome.

659
00:45:29,370 --> 00:45:31,080
Welcome to Class B.

660
00:45:47,870 --> 00:45:48,710
I'll go back then.

661
00:45:50,040 --> 00:45:50,880
Mhm.

662
00:45:51,410 --> 00:45:52,450
Thanks,

663
00:45:55,160 --> 00:45:56,000
Brother.

664
00:47:40,500 --> 00:47:41,500
Why are you avoiding me?

665
00:47:49,540 --> 00:47:51,250
Because you like Yang Jing?

666
00:47:56,750 --> 00:47:58,160
Or is it just for fun?

667
00:47:58,830 --> 00:47:59,670
Impulsive?

668
00:48:02,160 --> 00:48:03,410
Or regret?

669
00:48:04,000 --> 00:48:05,080
None of those.

670
00:48:12,200 --> 00:48:13,290
Then for what?

671
00:48:19,540 --> 00:48:21,080
Because I like you.

672
00:49:15,330 --> 00:49:16,330
New student,

673
00:49:16,330 --> 00:49:18,120
you can sit here for now.

674
00:49:18,120 --> 00:49:19,200
Wait.

675
00:49:29,870 --> 00:49:30,790
It's okay.

676
00:49:30,790 --> 00:49:32,160
You can take this one.

677
00:49:36,290 --> 00:49:37,450
Tian, what are you doing?

678
00:49:38,040 --> 00:49:39,000
Changing my seat.

679
00:49:40,860 --> 00:49:41,700
Yeah, I know.

680
00:49:41,700 --> 00:49:43,080
But why the sudden change?

681
00:49:45,910 --> 00:49:47,700
This has always been my seat.

682
00:49:49,700 --> 00:49:50,540
That's right.

683
00:49:50,950 --> 00:49:52,000
It's good you're here.

684
00:49:52,000 --> 00:49:54,540
Otherwise, if I get bored in class,
it'd be awkward

685
00:49:54,540 --> 00:49:56,080
with a stranger sitting behind me

686
00:49:56,080 --> 00:49:57,500
who won't talk to me, right?

687
00:50:00,540 --> 00:50:01,790
I won't talk to you either.

688
00:50:04,700 --> 00:50:05,540
True.

689
00:50:06,080 --> 00:50:08,580
Compared to you, Sheng is better.

690
00:50:30,540 --> 00:50:38,090
♪Your gaze cuts right through♪

691
00:50:38,960 --> 00:50:46,000
♪My hidden stubbornness and fragility♪

692
00:50:46,000 --> 00:50:53,090
♪Your breath turned my world
upside down♪

693
00:50:53,120 --> 00:50:54,620
(After Mom passed away,)

694
00:50:55,450 --> 00:50:57,120
(I've always been alone.)

695
00:50:57,950 --> 00:51:01,150
♪I want to be you♪

696
00:51:01,250 --> 00:51:03,530
(Even though I felt lonely and scared,)

697
00:51:03,540 --> 00:51:08,390
♪What exactly is our relationship♪

698
00:51:08,450 --> 00:51:10,040
(I never let anyone know)

699
00:51:10,790 --> 00:51:12,080
(or talked about it,)

700
00:51:18,700 --> 00:51:19,540
(until...)

701
00:51:19,540 --> 00:51:20,540
Jiang Tian!

702
00:51:26,200 --> 00:51:27,910
Actually, we can give it a try.

703
00:51:29,750 --> 00:51:30,590
Try what?

704
00:51:32,620 --> 00:51:34,040
Try getting closer.

705
00:51:38,790 --> 00:51:39,950
We both fought,

706
00:51:40,410 --> 00:51:41,790
so we should be punished equally.

707
00:51:41,790 --> 00:51:43,040
What do the two punks look like?

708
00:51:45,290 --> 00:51:46,130
Does it hurt?

709
00:51:49,330 --> 00:51:50,250
Are you scared?

710
00:51:56,840 --> 00:52:02,990
♪Please don't let go of my hand♪

711
00:52:03,000 --> 00:52:06,410
"In front I see
the slanting sun atop the hill.

712
00:52:06,410 --> 00:52:09,620
Turning my head,
I see the dreary beaten track.

713
00:52:09,620 --> 00:52:10,870
Let me go back.

714
00:52:10,870 --> 00:52:14,080
Impervious to wind, rain or shine,
I'll have my will."

715
00:52:14,790 --> 00:52:16,870
You all know this poem, right?

716
00:52:18,750 --> 00:52:22,500
"Calming the Waves"
is a famous work by Su Dongpo.

717
00:52:22,500 --> 00:52:25,620
At that time, he was exiled.

718
00:52:25,620 --> 00:52:29,410
He wrote to express his inner thoughts.

719
00:52:30,040 --> 00:52:32,700
He said he wouldn't be afraid

720
00:52:33,290 --> 00:52:35,160
and would march forward bravely

721
00:52:35,500 --> 00:52:37,000
without fear.

722
00:52:38,250 --> 00:52:40,120
He was also looking forward to

723
00:52:41,290 --> 00:52:42,750
the day he could return.

724
00:52:50,120 --> 00:52:51,200
(Sheng Wang,)

725
00:52:52,870 --> 00:52:54,080
(I'll be waiting for you.)

726
00:52:57,330 --> 00:52:59,410
(Loving someone in secret
stirs up one-sided chaos.)

727
00:53:00,120 --> 00:53:01,620
(Because I like you so much,)

728
00:53:02,250 --> 00:53:04,160
(I've been overly cautious,)

729
00:53:04,160 --> 00:53:05,500
(like treading on thin ice.)

730
00:53:06,750 --> 00:53:08,330
(But I almost forgot)

731
00:53:08,870 --> 00:53:10,250
(I'm only 17.)

732
00:53:11,790 --> 00:53:15,120
(At this age, the whole world is mine.)

733
00:53:15,660 --> 00:53:16,950
(There's no need to hesitate)

734
00:53:17,330 --> 00:53:18,830
(or weigh my options.)

735
00:53:19,580 --> 00:53:21,120
(I'm invincible.)

736
00:53:21,580 --> 00:53:23,000
(I can do anything.)

737
00:53:30,880 --> 00:53:34,800
♪I don't know what went wrong♪

738
00:53:34,800 --> 00:53:38,170
♪I shouldn't have let you go♪

739
00:53:38,170 --> 00:53:42,030
♪I want to say out loud to the world♪

740
00:53:42,910 --> 00:53:44,700
(Could you try to come back?)

741
00:53:46,540 --> 00:53:47,450
(Yes.)

742
00:54:01,350 --> 00:54:04,080
♪You came, and you left♪

743
00:54:04,660 --> 00:54:07,910
♪I loved, but I'm hurt♪

744
00:54:07,910 --> 00:54:14,160
♪Unable to embrace you, I fell♪

745
00:54:14,870 --> 00:54:17,830
♪I try to walk towards you♪

746
00:54:17,830 --> 00:54:21,450
♪Only to find you've been silently
behind me all along♪

747
00:54:21,450 --> 00:54:27,200
♪Like Night and Day residing in the Sky♪

748
00:54:28,200 --> 00:54:32,040
♪Where is the end of the story♪

749
00:54:32,040 --> 00:54:34,870
♪Who decides if it is love♪

750
00:54:34,870 --> 00:54:40,830
♪Such intimacy, no one can replace♪

751
00:54:40,830 --> 00:54:47,950
♪Our encounter
like the Milky Way's trajectory♪

752
00:54:47,950 --> 00:54:54,410
♪Cannot be avoided like this heavy rain♪

753
00:54:54,410 --> 00:55:01,540
♪Our youth like the frozen time♪

754
00:55:01,540 --> 00:55:08,080
♪This moment is eternity.
I run towards you♪

755
00:55:08,080 --> 00:55:14,970
♪In the dark valley,
you will catch my heart♪

756
00:55:28,950 --> 00:55:33,160
♪No one can escape destiny♪

757
00:55:33,160 --> 00:55:35,750
